title: 17. Eight things I've learned from having 6 kids
description:
Some things really get easier the more kids you have. In this episode, I'm sharing the things I let go, personality types and other things I've learned as a large-ish family mom. 

I'm already thinking of things I forget, so possibly there will be a part two.

Follow along with Farmhouse on Boone:

The blog

The Youtube channel

Instagram

Thanks again for listening and I'll see you in the next episode of the Simple Farmhouse Life podcast.
